
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xie-ps-centralized-address-management-02.txt'>
    <title>"Problem statement for centralized address management", Chongfeng Xie, Qiong Sun, Weiping Xu, Will LIU, Ian Farrer, Normen Kowalewski, Ying Cheng</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xie-ps-centralized-address-management-02.txt</link>
    <description>The increase in number, diversity and complexity of devices and services in modern networks bring new challenges for the management of network resources, such as IP addresses, network prefixes, bandwidth, and services that utilize such resources. This draft contains a problem statement for IP address management and defines requirements with practical use cases provided by operators.</description>
    <dc:date>2017-03-12T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
